<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>سَلاَمٌ عَلَى مَنِ اتَّبَعَ الهُدَى،<span class="c5"> أَمَّا بَعْد:</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>